         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="zoor0091.translation" corresp="#zoor0091.transcription">
            <p>Monument of Annes (or Anna), (son or daughter) of Sabbinianus (?), who died (at
                    the age) of ninety-one years, having a good name and good faith, in the year
                    300, on (the) 12th (day) of (the) month Hyperberetaios, on (the) 6th day of
                    (the) Lord (Friday). Be of good cheer, no one (is) immortal.</p>
